10509 {
10510  struct copy_stream_struct *stp = (struct copy_stream_struct *)arg;
10511  VALUE src_io = stp->src, dst_io = stp->dst;
10512  rb_io_t *src_fptr = 0, *dst_fptr = 0;
10513  int src_fd, dst_fd;
10514  const int common_oflags = 0
10515 #ifdef O_NOCTTY
10516  | O_NOCTTY
10517 #endif
10518  ;
10519 
10520  stp->th = rb_thread_current();
10521 
10522  stp->total = 0;
10523 
10524  if (src_io == argf) {
10525  src_fd = -1;
10526  }
10527  else if (RB_TYPE_P(src_io, T_FILE)) {
10528  goto io_src;
10529  }
10530  else if (!RB_TYPE_P(src_io, T_STRING) &&
10531  (rb_respond_to(src_io, id_read) ||
10532  rb_respond_to(src_io, id_readpartial))) {
10533  src_fd = -1;
10534  }
10535  else {
10536  VALUE args[2];
10537  FilePathValue(src_io);
10538  args[0] = src_io;
10539  args[1] = INT2NUM(O_RDONLY|common_oflags);
10540  src_io = rb_class_new_instance(2, args, rb_cFile);
10541  stp->src = src_io;
10542  stp->close_src = 1;
10543  io_src:
10544  GetOpenFile(src_io, src_fptr);
10545  rb_io_check_byte_readable(src_fptr);
10546  src_fd = src_fptr->fd;
10547  }
10548  stp->src_fd = src_fd;
10549 
10550  if (dst_io == argf) {
10551  dst_fd = -1;
10552  }
10553  else if (RB_TYPE_P(dst_io, T_FILE)) {
10554  dst_io = GetWriteIO(dst_io);
10555  stp->dst = dst_io;
10556  goto io_dst;
10557  }
10558  else if (!RB_TYPE_P(dst_io, T_STRING) &&
10559  rb_respond_to(dst_io, id_write)) {
10560  dst_fd = -1;
10561  }
10562  else {
10563  VALUE args[3];
10564  FilePathValue(dst_io);
10565  args[0] = dst_io;
10566  args[1] = INT2NUM(O_WRONLY|O_CREAT|O_TRUNC|common_oflags);
10567  args[2] = INT2FIX(0666);
10568  dst_io = rb_class_new_instance(3, args, rb_cFile);
10569  stp->dst = dst_io;
10570  stp->close_dst = 1;
10571  io_dst:
10572  GetOpenFile(dst_io, dst_fptr);
10573  rb_io_check_writable(dst_fptr);
10574  dst_fd = dst_fptr->fd;
10575  }
10576  stp->dst_fd = dst_fd;
10577 
10578 #ifdef O_BINARY
10579  if (src_fptr)
10580  SET_BINARY_MODE_WITH_SEEK_CUR(src_fptr);
10581 #endif
10582  if (dst_fptr)
10583  io_ascii8bit_binmode(dst_fptr);
10584 
10585  if (stp->src_offset == (off_t)-1 && src_fptr && src_fptr->rbuf.len) {
10586  size_t len = src_fptr->rbuf.len;
10587  VALUE str;
10588  if (stp->copy_length != (off_t)-1 && stp->copy_length < (off_t)len) {
10589  len = (size_t)stp->copy_length;
10590  }
10591  str = rb_str_buf_new(len);
10592  rb_str_resize(str,len);
10593  read_buffered_data(RSTRING_PTR(str), len, src_fptr);
10594  if (dst_fptr) { /* IO or filename */
10595  if (io_binwrite(str, RSTRING_PTR(str), RSTRING_LEN(str), dst_fptr, 0) < 0)
10596  rb_sys_fail(0);
10597  }
10598  else /* others such as StringIO */
10599  rb_io_write(dst_io, str);
10600  stp->total += len;
10601  if (stp->copy_length != (off_t)-1)
10602  stp->copy_length -= len;
10603  }
10604 
10605  if (dst_fptr && io_fflush(dst_fptr) < 0) {
10606  rb_raise(rb_eIOError, "flush failed");
10607  }
10608 
10609  if (stp->copy_length == 0)
10610  return Qnil;
10611 
10612  if (src_fd == -1 || dst_fd == -1) {
10613  return copy_stream_fallback(stp);
10614  }
10615 
10616  rb_fd_set(src_fd, &stp->fds);
10617  rb_fd_set(dst_fd, &stp->fds);
10618 
10619  rb_thread_call_without_gvl(nogvl_copy_stream_func, (void*)stp, RUBY_UBF_IO, 0);

10621 }

10467

10469  break;
10470  }

10475  rb_str_resize(buf, ss > 0 ? ss : 0);
10476  if (ss == -1)
10477  return Qnil;
10478  if (ss == 0)
10479  rb_eof_error();
10480  if (off != (off_t)-1)
10481  off += ss;
10482  }
10483  n = rb_io_write(stp->dst, buf);
10484  numwrote = NUM2LONG(n);
10485  stp->total += numwrote;
10486  rest -= numwrote;
10487  if (read_method == id_read && RSTRING_LEN(buf) == 0) {
10488  break;
10489  }
10490  }
10491 
10492  return Qnil;
10493 }

12404  * as command-line arguments or passed in via STDIN.
12405  *
12406  * See ARGF (the class) for more details.
12407  */
12408  rb_define_global_const("ARGF", argf);
12409 
12410  rb_define_hooked_variable("$.", &argf, argf_lineno_getter, argf_lineno_setter);
12411  rb_define_hooked_variable("$FILENAME", &argf, argf_filename_getter, rb_gvar_readonly_setter);
12412  ARGF.filename = rb_str_new2("-");
12413 
12414  rb_define_hooked_variable("$-i", &argf, opt_i_get, opt_i_set);
12415  rb_define_hooked_variable("$*", &argf, argf_argv_getter, rb_gvar_readonly_setter);
12416 
12417 #if defined (_WIN32) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
12418  atexit(pipe_atexit);
12419 #endif
12420

12422

1772  fptr->rbuf.len = (int)r; /* r should be <= rbuf_capa */
1773  if (r == 0)
1774  return -1; /* EOF */
1775  }
1776  return 0;
1777 }

762  if (len > min_capa)
763  fptr->rbuf.capa = (int)len;
764  else
765  fptr->rbuf.capa = min_capa;
766  fptr->rbuf.ptr = ALLOC_N(char, fptr->rbuf.capa);
767  }
768  if (fptr->rbuf.capa < len + fptr->rbuf.len) {
769  rb_raise(rb_eIOError, "ungetbyte failed");
770  }
771  if (fptr->rbuf.off < len) {
772  MEMMOVE(fptr->rbuf.ptr+fptr->rbuf.capa-fptr->rbuf.len,
773  fptr->rbuf.ptr+fptr->rbuf.off,
774  char, fptr->rbuf.len);
775  fptr->rbuf.off = fptr->rbuf.capa-fptr->rbuf.len;
776  }
777  fptr->rbuf.off-=(int)len;
778  fptr->rbuf.len+=(int)len;
779  MEMMOVE(fptr->rbuf.ptr+fptr->rbuf.off, RSTRING_PTR(str), char, len);
780 }

6039  rb_io_synchronized(RFILE(orig_stdout)->fptr);
6040  rb_io_synchronized(RFILE(orig_stderr)->fptr);
6041  return Qnil;
6042  }
6043 # else
6044  rb_notimplement();
6045 # endif
6046  }
6047 
6048  /* parent */
6049  if (pid == -1) {
6050 # if defined(HAVE_WORKING_FORK)
6051  e = errno;
6052 # endif
6053  close(arg.pair[0]);
6054  close(arg.pair[1]);
6055  if ((fmode & (FMODE_READABLE|FMODE_WRITABLE)) == (FMODE_READABLE|FMODE_WRITABLE)) {
6056  close(arg.write_pair[0]);
6057  close(arg.write_pair[1]);
6058  }
6059  errno = e;
6060 # if defined(HAVE_WORKING_FORK)
6061  if (errmsg[0])
6062  rb_sys_fail(errmsg);
6063 # endif
6064  rb_sys_fail_str(prog);
6065  }
6066  if ((fmode & FMODE_READABLE) && (fmode & FMODE_WRITABLE)) {
6067  close(arg.pair[1]);
6068  fd = arg.pair[0];
6069  close(arg.write_pair[0]);
6070  write_fd = arg.write_pair[1];
6071  }
6072  else if (fmode & FMODE_READABLE) {
6073  close(arg.pair[1]);
6074  fd = arg.pair[0];
6075  }
6076  else {
6077  close(arg.pair[0]);
6078  fd = arg.pair[1];
6079  }
6080 #else
6081  if (argc) {
6082  prog = rb_ary_join(rb_ary_new4(argc, argv), rb_str_new2(" "));
6083  cmd = StringValueCStr(prog);
6084  }
6085  if (!NIL_P(execarg_obj)) {
6086  rb_execarg_parent_start(execarg_obj);
6087  rb_execarg_run_options(eargp, sargp, NULL, 0);
6088  }
6089  fp = popen(cmd, modestr);
6090  if (eargp) {
6091  rb_execarg_parent_end(execarg_obj);
6092  rb_execarg_run_options(sargp, NULL, NULL, 0);
6093  }
6094  if (!fp) rb_sys_fail_path(prog);
6095  fd = fileno(fp);
6096 #endif
6097 
6098  port = io_alloc(rb_cIO);
6099  MakeOpenFile(port, fptr);
6100  fptr->fd = fd;
6101  fptr->stdio_file = fp;
6102  fptr->mode = fmode | FMODE_SYNC|FMODE_DUPLEX;
6103  if (convconfig) {
6104  fptr->encs = *convconfig;
6105 #if defined(RUBY_TEST_CRLF_ENVIRONMENT) || defined(_WIN32)
6106  if (fptr->encs.ecflags & ECONV_DEFAULT_NEWLINE_DECORATOR) {
6107  fptr->encs.ecflags |= ECONV_UNIVERSAL_NEWLINE_DECORATOR;
6108  }
6109 #endif
6110  }
6111  else {
6112  if (NEED_NEWLINE_DECORATOR_ON_READ(fptr)) {
6113  fptr->encs.ecflags |= ECONV_UNIVERSAL_NEWLINE_DECORATOR;
6114  }
6115 #ifdef TEXTMODE_NEWLINE_DECORATOR_ON_WRITE
6116  if (NEED_NEWLINE_DECORATOR_ON_WRITE(fptr)) {
6117  fptr->encs.ecflags |= TEXTMODE_NEWLINE_DECORATOR_ON_WRITE;
6118  }
6119 #endif
6120  }
6121  fptr->pid = pid;
6122 
6123  if (0 <= write_fd) {
6124  write_port = io_alloc(rb_cIO);
6125  MakeOpenFile(write_port, write_fptr);
6126  write_fptr->fd = write_fd;
6127  write_fptr->mode = (fmode & ~FMODE_READABLE)| FMODE_SYNC|FMODE_DUPLEX;
6128  fptr->mode &= ~FMODE_WRITABLE;
6129  fptr->tied_io_for_writing = write_port;
6130  rb_ivar_set(port, rb_intern("@tied_io_for_writing"), write_port);
6131  }
6132 
6133 #if defined (__CYGWIN__) || !defined(HAVE_WORKING_FORK)
6134  fptr->finalize = pipe_finalize;
6135  pipe_add_fptr(fptr);
6136 #endif
6137  return port;
6138 }

3726  fptr->encs.enc);
3727  else
3728  r = ONIGENC_CONSTRUCT_MBCLEN_CHARFOUND(1);
3729  if (!MBCLEN_NEEDMORE_P(r))
3730  break;
3731  if (fptr->cbuf.len == fptr->cbuf.capa) {
3732  rb_raise(rb_eIOError, "too long character");
3733  }
3734  }
3735  if (more_char(fptr) == MORE_CHAR_FINISHED) {
3736  clear_readconv(fptr);
3737  /* ignore an incomplete character before EOF */
3738  return io;
3739  }
3740  }
3741  if (MBCLEN_INVALID_P(r)) {
3742  rb_raise(rb_eArgError, "invalid byte sequence in %s",
3743  rb_enc_name(fptr->encs.enc));
3744  }
3745  n = MBCLEN_CHARFOUND_LEN(r);
3746  if (fptr->encs.enc) {
3747  c = rb_enc_codepoint(fptr->cbuf.ptr+fptr->cbuf.off,
3748  fptr->cbuf.ptr+fptr->cbuf.off+fptr->cbuf.len,
3749  fptr->encs.enc);
3750  }
3751  else {
3752  c = (unsigned char)fptr->cbuf.ptr[fptr->cbuf.off];
3753  }
3754  fptr->cbuf.off += n;
3755  fptr->cbuf.len -= n;
3756  rb_yield(UINT2NUM(c));
3757  }
3758  }
3759  NEED_NEWLINE_DECORATOR_ON_READ_CHECK(fptr);
3760  enc = io_input_encoding(fptr);
3761  while (io_fillbuf(fptr) >= 0) {
3762  r = rb_enc_precise_mbclen(fptr->rbuf.ptr+fptr->rbuf.off,
3763  fptr->rbuf.ptr+fptr->rbuf.off+fptr->rbuf.len, enc);
3764  if (MBCLEN_CHARFOUND_P(r) &&
3765  (n = MBCLEN_CHARFOUND_LEN(r)) <= fptr->rbuf.len) {
3766  c = rb_enc_codepoint(fptr->rbuf.ptr+fptr->rbuf.off,
3767  fptr->rbuf.ptr+fptr->rbuf.off+fptr->rbuf.len, enc);
3768  fptr->rbuf.off += n;
3769  fptr->rbuf.len -= n;
3770  rb_yield(UINT2NUM(c));
3771  }
3772  else if (MBCLEN_INVALID_P(r)) {
3773  rb_raise(rb_eArgError, "invalid byte sequence in %s", rb_enc_name(enc));
3774  }
3775  else {
3776  continue;
3777  }
3778  }
3779  return io;
3780 }

3231  * extra_limit limits the relax length */
3232  limit = 1;

7581  int ofmode;
7582 #else
7583  struct stat st;
7584 #endif
7585 
7586

7588  rb_io_extract_modeenc(&vmode, 0, opt, &oflags, &fmode, &convconfig);
7589 
7590  fd = NUM2INT(fnum);
7591  if (rb_reserved_fd_p(fd)) {
7592  rb_raise(rb_eArgError, "The given fd is not accessible because RubyVM reserves it");
7593  }
7594 #if defined(HAVE_FCNTL) && defined(F_GETFL)
7595  oflags = fcntl(fd, F_GETFL);
7596  if (oflags == -1) rb_sys_fail(0);
7597 #else
7598  if (fstat(fd, &st) == -1) rb_sys_fail(0);
7599 #endif

7601 #if defined(HAVE_FCNTL) && defined(F_GETFL)
7602  ofmode = rb_io_oflags_fmode(oflags);
7603  if (NIL_P(vmode)) {
7604  fmode = ofmode;
7605  }
7606  else if ((~ofmode & fmode) & FMODE_READWRITE) {
7607  VALUE error = INT2FIX(EINVAL);
7608  rb_exc_raise(rb_class_new_instance(1, &error, rb_eSystemCallError));
7609  }
7610 #endif
7611  if (!NIL_P(opt) && rb_hash_aref(opt, sym_autoclose) == Qfalse) {
7612  fmode |= FMODE_PREP;
7613  }
7614  MakeOpenFile(io, fp);
7615  fp->fd = fd;
7616  fp->mode = fmode;
7617  fp->encs = convconfig;
7618  clear_codeconv(fp);
7619  io_check_tty(fp);
7620  if (fileno(stdin) == fd)
7621  fp->stdio_file = stdin;
7622  else if (fileno(stdout) == fd)
7623  fp->stdio_file = stdout;
7624  else if (fileno(stderr) == fd)
7625  fp->stdio_file = stderr;
7626 
7627  if (fmode & FMODE_SETENC_BY_BOM) io_set_encoding_by_bom(io);
7628  return io;
7629 }

218 {
219  /* MinGW don't have F_GETFD and FD_CLOEXEC. [ruby-core:40281] */
220 #if defined(HAVE_FCNTL) && defined(F_GETFD) && defined(F_SETFD) && defined(FD_CLOEXEC)
221  int flags, flags2, ret;
222  flags = fcntl(fd, F_GETFD); /* should not fail except EBADF. */
223  if (flags == -1) {
224  rb_bug("rb_maygvl_fd_fix_cloexec: fcntl(%d, F_GETFD) failed: %s", fd, strerror(errno));
225  }
226  if (fd <= 2)
227  flags2 = flags & ~FD_CLOEXEC; /* Clear CLOEXEC for standard file descriptors: 0, 1, 2. */
228  else
229  flags2 = flags | FD_CLOEXEC; /* Set CLOEXEC for non-standard file descriptors: 3, 4, 5, ... */
230  if (flags != flags2) {
231  ret = fcntl(fd, F_SETFD, flags2);
232  if (ret == -1) {
233  rb_bug("rb_maygvl_fd_fix_cloexec: fcntl(%d, F_SETFD, %d) failed: %s", fd, flags2, strerror(errno));

8380  if (READ_DATA_PENDING(fptr) || READ_CHAR_PENDING(fptr)) { /* check for buffered data */
8381  pending++;
8382  rb_fd_set(fptr->fd, &fds[3]);
8383  }
8384  if (max < fptr->fd) max = fptr->fd;
8385  }
8386  if (pending) { /* no blocking if there's buffered data */
8387  timerec.tv_sec = timerec.tv_usec = 0;
8388  tp = &timerec;
8389  }
8390  rp = &fds[0];
8391  }
8392  else
8393  rp = 0;
8394 
8395  if (!NIL_P(write)) {
8396  Check_Type(write, T_ARRAY);
8397  for (i=0; i<RARRAY_LEN(write); i++) {
8398  VALUE write_io = GetWriteIO(rb_io_get_io(RARRAY_AREF(write, i)));
8399  GetOpenFile(write_io, fptr);
8400  rb_fd_set(fptr->fd, &fds[1]);
8401  if (max < fptr->fd) max = fptr->fd;
8402  }
8403  wp = &fds[1];
8404  }
8405  else
8406  wp = 0;
8407 
8408  if (!NIL_P(except)) {
8409  Check_Type(except, T_ARRAY);
8410  for (i=0; i<RARRAY_LEN(except); i++) {
8411  VALUE io = rb_io_get_io(RARRAY_AREF(except, i));
8412  VALUE write_io = GetWriteIO(io);
8413  GetOpenFile(io, fptr);
8414  rb_fd_set(fptr->fd, &fds[2]);
8415  if (max < fptr->fd) max = fptr->fd;
8416  if (io != write_io) {
8417  GetOpenFile(write_io, fptr);
8418  rb_fd_set(fptr->fd, &fds[2]);
8419  if (max < fptr->fd) max = fptr->fd;
8420  }
8421  }
8422  ep = &fds[2];
8423  }
8424  else {
8425  ep = 0;
8426  }
8427 
8428  max++;
8429 
8430  n = rb_thread_fd_select(max, rp, wp, ep, tp);
8431  if (n < 0) {
8432  rb_sys_fail(0);
8433  }
8434  if (!pending && n == 0) return Qnil; /* returns nil on timeout */
8435 
8436  res = rb_ary_new2(3);
8437  rb_ary_push(res, rp?rb_ary_new():rb_ary_new2(0));
8438  rb_ary_push(res, wp?rb_ary_new():rb_ary_new2(0));
8439  rb_ary_push(res, ep?rb_ary_new():rb_ary_new2(0));
8440 
8441  if (rp) {
8442  list = RARRAY_AREF(res, 0);
8443  for (i=0; i< RARRAY_LEN(read); i++) {
8444  VALUE obj = rb_ary_entry(read, i);
8445  VALUE io = rb_io_get_io(obj);
8446  GetOpenFile(io, fptr);
8447  if (rb_fd_isset(fptr->fd, &fds[0]) ||
8448  rb_fd_isset(fptr->fd, &fds[3])) {
8449  rb_ary_push(list, obj);
8450  }
8451  }
8452  }
8453 
8454  if (wp) {
8455  list = RARRAY_AREF(res, 1);

8457  VALUE obj = rb_ary_entry(write, i);
8458  VALUE io = rb_io_get_io(obj);
8459  VALUE write_io = GetWriteIO(io);

8461  if (rb_fd_isset(fptr->fd, &fds[1])) {
8462  rb_ary_push(list, obj);
8463  }
8464  }
8465  }
8466

8468  list = RARRAY_AREF(res, 2);

8470  VALUE obj = rb_ary_entry(except, i);

8476  }

8478  GetOpenFile(write_io, fptr);
8479  if (rb_fd_isset(fptr->fd, &fds[2])) {
8480  rb_ary_push(list, obj);
8481  }
8482  }
8483  }
8484  }
8485 
8486  return res; /* returns an empty array on interrupt */
